                                "description": "### Update profile details\n\n#### Request Body Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Required | Description | Constraints |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `name` | `string` | Yes | Updated full name of the user. | Max Length: `255` |\n| `email` | `string` | Yes | Updated email address. Must be unique. | Max Length: `255` |\n| `password` | `string \/ null` | No | Optional new password (must be confirmed). | - |\n| `password_confirmation` | `string \/ null` | No | Password confirmation (required if password is provided, must match password). | - |\n\n### Responses\n\n#### Response: `200`\n\n\n```json\n{\n    \"message\": \"ab\",\n    \"user\": {\n        \"id\": 74,\n        \"name\": \"et consequuntur et\",\n        \"email\": null,\n        \"email_verified_at\": \"2000-04-08T14:18:20+00:00\",\n        \"role\": \"sint\",\n        \"is_active\": true,\n        \"created_at\": \"2010-10-04T04:55:15+00:00\",\n        \"updated_at\": \"2016-04-07T21:49:57+00:00\"\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### Response: `403`\nAttempting to access a route or perform an action without the required user role or permissions.\n\n```json\n{\n    \"error_code\": \"FORBIDDEN\",\n    \"exception_type\": \"AuthorizationException\",\n    \"message\": \"You do not have permission to perform this action.\"\n}\n```\n\n#### Response: `401`\nRequesting protected routes without a valid JWT token, or token is expired\/invalid.\n\n```json\n{\n    \"error_code\": \"UNAUTHENTICATED\",\n    \"exception_type\": \"AuthenticationException\",\n    \"message\": \"You are not authenticated. Please provide a valid token.\"\n}\n```\n\n#### Response: `422`\nValidation error\n\n```json\n{\n    \"error_code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n    \"message\": \"The given data was invalid.\",\n    \"errors\": []\n}\n```\n\n",
